                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.11L5232/571: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Germany</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Mayer</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-05-13T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 13, 1936—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>51. Your 143, May 12, 5 p.m. Department approves your action and considers that
                    no further action by you is called for. Commission is now hearing arguments.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
